item.title: CVE-2017-16173|2024-09-16T22:56:37.124Z -- hackerone -- utahcityfinder%20node%20module
item.description: utahcityfinder constructs lists of Utah cities with a certain prefix. utahcityfinder is vulnerable to a directory traversal issue, giving an attacker access to the filesystem by placing "../" in the url.
